Create a manually triggered cloud flow that:

1. Initializes these variables: varRCCount (Integer, 0), varImportCycleID (String, empty), varRCFileID (String, empty)

2. Lists files in OneDrive for Business folder /00.EMS/EMS/Inbox/ReferenceControls

3. If folder has files:
   - Sets varRCFileID to first file ID
   - Creates a new row in Dataverse table "Import Cycles" with Cycle Name = current month, Status = Draft, Triggered By = "Power Automate"
   - Sets varImportCycleID to the new record ID
   - Reads Excel file using Excel Online Business connector, table name "Referencecontrols" with columns: Reference Control ID, Reference Control Title, Reference Control Description
   - For each row: Upserts into Dataverse table "Reference Controls" matching on Reference Control Identifier field
   - Increments varRCCount
   - Moves file to /00.EMS/EMS/Archive/ReferenceControls

4. Updates Import Cycle row with Reference Controls Imported = varRCCount
